-	Involvement in proposal pitches and working closely with the Creative and Design teams to develop a winning proposal, working on costing, and presentation to clients; 
-	Pre-event preparation;  
-	Site preparation;  
-	Project costing and budget management;  
-	Handle and oversee end-to-end development and implementation of all events allocated, including local and overseas events;  
